					<p>Capti Voice utilizes the unique concept of playlists to make content distribution simple and effective for teachers and administrators. Rather than relying on separate document sharing sites to distribute content, teachers using Capti can easily select which students they’d like to view the playlist they created and even link exams to different playlists to make reference materials more accessible. This method of sharing allows teachers and administrators to share pdfs, books, and other reading and research materials online.</p>

